WEBVTT

00:04.070 --> 00:07.373
Man: I've lived in
Washington, D.C., for 20 years.

00:07.441 --> 00:09.976
It's where I met Dean,
playing pick-up basketball,

00:10.043 --> 00:11.644
And made a life
for myself.

00:13.280 --> 00:16.682
But no matter how long
you've been away from home

00:16.750 --> 00:19.418
Or how much you've changed,
the place where you were

00:19.486 --> 00:22.822
Born and raised always stays
somewhere deep inside.

00:22.890 --> 00:24.790
For me, that place
was Oil City,

00:24.858 --> 00:26.926
A small town
with small-town values

00:26.994 --> 00:29.428
In the hills
of western Pennsylvania.

