you go like that.

10:01.468 --> 10:03.902
So you try it.
Film something.

10:03.970 --> 10:05.170
That's awesome.

10:05.238 --> 10:07.673
I was hoping c.J.
Would use his new camera

10:07.740 --> 10:09.274
to shine some light

10:09.342 --> 10:12.010
on what life was like
for him as a gay teen.

10:12.078 --> 10:14.613
For practice, I asked him
to join us at a concert

10:14.681 --> 10:17.683
I helped to organize
featuring Namoli Brennet.

10:17.750 --> 10:19.785
Namoli's a transgendered
musician.

10:19.853 --> 10:23.122
She's also from a small town
and lives her life very openly.

10:23.189 --> 10:26.158
Maybe it was
the activist in me,

10:26.226 --> 10:27.860
but I thought she might
be an inspiration

10:27.927 --> 10:29.294
for folks in Oil City.

