11:41.668 --> 11:44.603
Wilson: The biggest event
of the year in Oil City

11:44.671 --> 11:46.505
is the oil heritage parade.

11:46.573 --> 11:48.407
Most people come out
to watch their kids March

11:48.474 --> 11:50.242
or their friends ride around
silly floats.

11:50.310 --> 11:53.345
Even in the pouring rain.

11:53.413 --> 11:56.448
So I wasn't expecting to see
an anti-gay marriage protest

11:56.516 --> 11:58.550
led by none other
than Diane Gramley

11:58.618 --> 12:00.619
of the American
Family Association.

12:00.687 --> 12:02.454
She'd already refused
several requests

12:02.522 --> 12:04.022
to be formally interviewed,

12:04.090 --> 12:05.857
so I tried a more
direct approach.

12:05.925 --> 12:07.392
Hi, Diane.
How are you?

12:07.460 --> 12:08.627
Fine, and you?

12:08.695 --> 12:10.829
I'm not going to be part
of your documentary.

12:10.897 --> 12:12.698
Yeah, we just wanted
to know why

12:12.765 --> 12:14.199
You're so actively seeking

12:14.267 --> 12:16.668
to discriminate against
gay and lesbian people.

12:16.736 --> 12:18.437
We talked about it
on the phone.

12:18.504 --> 12:20.105
Well, why do you think
that they don't deserve

12:20.173 --> 12:23.709
to live freely
in society as you do?

12:23.776 --> 12:25.644
They have every right
to live freely,

12:25.712 --> 12:27.613
and they are living
freely in society.

12:27.680 --> 12:29.881
I would like to know why
you encourage children

12:29.949 --> 12:31.883
to participate in
a dangerous lifestyle.

12:31.951 --> 12:33.352
Hey, Joe,
how you doing?

12:33.419 --> 12:35.020
Good, and you?
Nice to see you.

12:35.088 --> 12:36.688
Good seeing you.
Yeah.

12:36.756 --> 12:38.390
Gramley: There've been
homosexuals throughout society,

12:38.458 --> 12:39.725
but they have not attempted

12:39.792 --> 12:42.427
to redefine marriage
and family as they are today.

12:42.495 --> 12:44.196
Everything else with gay
people is okay, right?

12:44.264 --> 12:45.731
They can teach school.

12:45.798 --> 12:47.733
If they have a job,
and they're doing their job,

12:47.800 --> 12:49.434
they have every right
to have that job.

12:49.502 --> 12:51.303
And they could be out on
the job and tell people

12:51.371 --> 12:52.771
