13:29.976 --> 13:33.111
Woman: Any other
business to enter?

13:33.179 --> 13:36.081
My name's --
oh, I'm sorry.

13:36.149 --> 13:38.350
Please state your name
for the record.

13:40.353 --> 13:41.753
My name is Kathy Springer.

13:41.821 --> 13:43.855
Have you implemented,

13:43.923 --> 13:46.158
