and how it was handled.

13:56.703 --> 13:59.905
Are you -- is there a better
way of handling things?

13:59.972 --> 14:02.674
Man: Ma'am, do me a favor.
Will you give me a call?

14:02.742 --> 14:05.577
Okay? This isn't
the time to --

14:05.645 --> 14:08.113
I just, as a taxpayer,
wanted to know if --

14:08.181 --> 14:10.782
you know, should I decide
to send my son back?

14:10.850 --> 14:12.884
Are there going
to be any changes?

14:12.952 --> 14:14.386
That's all.

14:14.454 --> 14:16.688
There have been
discussions taking place,

14:16.723 --> 14:18.523
and there
have been issues

14:18.591 --> 14:20.992
not only with myself
and Mr. Richmond,

14:21.060 --> 14:23.595
Mr. Forrester,
and the other principals,

14:23.663 --> 14:26.298
so I don't know
if that's --

14:26.366 --> 14:29.434
But, please, feel free
to give me a call, okay?

14:29.502 --> 14:31.603
It was like, "oh, god,

14:31.671 --> 14:35.240
give her her five minutes
and get her out of here."

14:35.308 --> 14:38.877
I really don't see that they've
seen us as a threat or anything.

14:38.945 --> 14:40.712
We were just an annoyance.

14:40.780 --> 14:42.047
Mm-hmm.

14:42.115 --> 14:43.682
Wilson: Shortly after
kathy's appearance,

14:43.750 --> 14:45.917
the school board did
propose a plan

14:45.985 --> 14:48.587
for inclusive
anti-discrimination training.

14:48.654 --> 14:50.989
But there was suddenly
an unusual amount

14:51.057 --> 14:53.024
of opposition from
the community,

14:53.092 --> 14:55.527
especially from
an African-American Pastor

14:55.595 --> 14:58.163
who wanted the training
to focus only on race

14:58.231 --> 15:00.565
and not even mention
sexual orientation.

15:00.633 --> 15:02.367
A <i>Derrick</i> reporter discovered

15:02.435 --> 15:04.603
the reason for
the racial outcry.

15:04.670 --> 15:07.806
Diane Gramley had sent out
another action alert.

15:07.874 --> 15:10.075
This one accused
the school district

15:10.143 --> 15:13.445
of trying to hijack civil rights
to promote homosexuality.

15:13.513 --> 15:17.082
The diversity training
never happened.

15:17.150 --> 15:19.985
I have to admit,
in this environment,

15:20.052 --> 15:21.820
it was a clever strategy

15:21.888 --> 15:24.790
to pit one minority group
against another.

15:24.857 --> 15:26.491
I'll tell you
what we're doing.

15:26.559 --> 15:28.260
We got married
a couple years ago,

15:28.327 --> 15:30.629
and we put our wedding
announcement in the paper,

15:30.696 --> 15:33.265
and it turned into this, like,
controversy or whatever.

15:33.332 --> 15:35.367
I got beat up
about a month ago.

15:35.435 --> 15:37.202
What?
Oh, yeah.

15:37.270 --> 15:40.505
I never thought people
were racist or anything.

15:40.573 --> 15:44.075
I'm Arab, and this girl
