15:47.680 --> 15:49.981
There was blood
all over me.

15:50.049 --> 15:51.750
I didn't have a chance.

15:51.818 --> 15:53.485
This place is rough.

15:53.553 --> 15:56.054
If you are not a man

15:56.122 --> 15:57.589
with white skin

15:57.657 --> 16:00.859
and who likes to do
the missionary position,

16:00.927 --> 16:02.627
it's over.

16:06.532 --> 16:08.533
