that interaction

18:57.136 --> 18:59.604
That I think he needs.

18:59.672 --> 19:01.873
Wilson: I was hoping
that the camera

19:01.941 --> 19:03.541
would help c.J.'s education.

19:03.609 --> 19:05.243
I asked him to film something

19:05.311 --> 19:07.545
