intellectual next time.

19:07.613 --> 19:10.782
Hitchcock: You know, one thing
about living in a small town

19:10.850 --> 19:13.284
is that the gene pool
is so limited.

19:13.352 --> 19:17.155
You know, trying to meet
somebody is really hard.

19:17.223 --> 19:19.591
Wilson: So who's this special
