how excited you were

19:24.664 --> 19:26.297
when I talked to you
on the phone,

19:26.365 --> 19:28.033
and you said,
"oh, I met somebody."

19:28.100 --> 19:29.734
Henderson: Well,
the cool part about it

19:29.802 --> 19:31.670
