19:38.210 --> 19:42.147
I've been telling people
I have a family now.

19:42.214 --> 19:44.916
Hitchcock: In some ways, she's
the total opposite of me.

19:44.984 --> 19:47.786
You know, I can be aggressive
and antagonistic,

19:47.853 --> 19:50.055
and she's just kind of quiet
and the peacemaker,

19:50.122 --> 19:53.658
and she's just calm.

19:53.726 --> 19:56.828
And she's very gifted.
