20:58.691 --> 21:00.558
It wasn't even
into the 200s.

21:00.626 --> 21:02.160
[ laughs ]

21:02.228 --> 21:05.330
Still have to get a new
exhaust, battery, tires,

21:05.397 --> 21:08.333
the title transferred,
my license,

21:08.400 --> 21:10.702
and then I'll be
on the road.

21:12.671 --> 21:15.140
I don't think I'll
probably ever be able

21:15.207 --> 21:17.308
to, like, walk down
through the streets

21:17.376 --> 21:18.977
of anywhere around here.

21:19.044 --> 21:21.246
I used to have, like,
a reputation and stuff

21:21.313 --> 21:23.014
