21:34.326 --> 21:36.795
Nothing, really.

21:36.862 --> 21:38.930
Eventually,
once in a while, wondering

21:38.998 --> 21:42.400
if this thing will actually
ever leave this garage.

21:49.909 --> 21:52.010
Hey. How are you?

21:52.077 --> 21:53.978
Wilson: I wasn't sure
if we would hear

21:54.046 --> 21:55.580
from Pastor Micklos again,

21:55.648 --> 21:58.583
but when he called to invite us
to lunch with his family,

21:58.651 --> 22:01.186
