where it would lead.

22:01.253 --> 22:03.588
When you contacted me
or I contacted you

22:03.656 --> 22:05.256
or however it occurred,

22:05.324 --> 22:07.158
one of the things
that I prayed

22:07.226 --> 22:09.527
