to view the world, you know.

22:15.401 --> 22:17.702
But can we,
at some point though,

22:17.770 --> 22:19.904
get to a point where
we respect that

22:19.972 --> 22:21.573
and respect each other?

22:21.640 --> 22:23.508
Well, no.

22:23.576 --> 22:25.109
