I was just happy for you.

23:43.055 --> 23:45.957
I could never

23:46.025 --> 23:48.126
deny who I am.

23:48.193 --> 23:50.895
I couldn't deny it.

23:50.963 --> 23:52.630
I was trying to find
ways around it,

23:52.698 --> 23:54.499
but people kept
directing the question,

23:54.566 --> 23:56.601
"are you gay?" to my face.

23:56.669 --> 23:59.470
I didn't know what to say,
but I couldn't deny who I was,

23:59.538 --> 24:01.239
so I ended up having --

24:01.307 --> 24:05.643
I ended up saying that,
"you know what, yeah.

24:05.711 --> 24:09.747
So what is it to you?
Big deal."

24:09.815 --> 24:14.185
And I guess it was
a big deal to everybody.

24:14.253 --> 24:17.155
I know that everybody cared
because at that day,

24:17.222 --> 24:18.923
everybody began to hate.

24:18.991 --> 24:22.260
I was no longer anybody
that anyone liked.

24:22.328 --> 24:24.996
Everybody hated c.J. Bills.

24:30.736 --> 24:33.304
Henderson: It's actually
rather phenomenal,

24:33.372 --> 24:36.074
